Package jadex.testcases.misc

This package contains miscellaneous testcases.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AMSTestPlan Test the AMS plans.
ArgumentsPlan Test if arguments can be accessed.
ArgumentsWorkerPlan Plan that sends back a message to the creator.
BeliefChangeCatchPlan Test if plan can be invoked when trigger is added dynamically at runtime.
CallbackPlan Test agent callbacks.
ConfigElementRefPlan Check naming of initial and end elements using config element ref worker agent.
ConfigElementRefWorkerPlan Check if the initial and end elements are correctly named.
DFTestPlan Test the df plans.
DynamicModelCreationPlan This plan dynamically creates a belief, goal and a plan.
DynamicTriggerPlan Test a dynamically added trigger.
EndStateInitiatorPlan Check correct operation of end states.
EndStatePlan Check correct operation of end states.
EndStateWorkerPlan Check correct operation of end states.
EndStateWorkerTestPlan Plan to react to various end elements.
ExpressionParameterPlan Test some expressions.
GuiOpenClosePlan Tests to open and close a gui.
InitialTransactionPlan Test if initial transaction works.
LeakerPlan Test memory consumption.
ParameterProtectionPlan The print plan simply prints out the object it gets as parameter in the construtor.
Person Simple person class with a name and an address.
RepeatabilityPlan Change some beliefs and belief sets in an atomic block, to trigger several conditions.
SerializationPlan Serialize the agent and write it to a file.
TriggerPlan A plan to be triggered by conditions of the repeatability test agent.
WaitForPlan Test various waitFor methods first from plan, then from external access.
